<DOC><DOCNO> WSJ870911-0156 </DOCNO><HL> Dividend News:First Financial Bancorp</HL><DD> 09/11/87</DD><SO> WALL STREET JOURNAL (J)</SO><IN> FFBCDIVIDENDS (DIV) </IN><TEXT>   FIRST FINANCIAL BANCORP declared a 3-for-2 stock split, payable Oct. 1 to stock of record Sept. 11. Directors also declared a quarterly dividend of 40 cents on pre-split shares, payable Oct. 1 to stock of record Sept. 10. The stock split will increase to 3,463,164 the number of common shares outstanding for the Monroe, Ohio-based bank holding company. </TEXT></DOC>